  <Milira_PlasmaMG.verbs.Verb_ChargeShoot.label>离子急射机枪</Milira_PlasmaMG.verbs.Verb_ChargeShoot.label>
  
  <!-- EN: plasma pistol -->
  <Milira_PlasmaPistol.label>离子手枪</Milira_PlasmaPistol.label>
  <!-- EN: A small launcher capable of quickly firing ion beams. The fired ion beams can melt the armor of target.\nChargeable.\nCan switch between rapid mode and scatter mode. -->
  <Milira_PlasmaPistol.description>能够快速发射离子束的小型发射器，发射的离子束能够融毁命中单位的护甲。\n\n可以充能。\n\n可以在速射模式和散射模式之间切换。</Milira_PlasmaPistol.description>
  <!-- EN: Switch to scatter mode. -->
  <Milira_PlasmaPistol.comps.CompRangeWeaponVerbSwitch.gizmoDesc1>当前为速射模式，点击切换至散射模式。</Milira_PlasmaPistol.comps.CompRangeWeaponVerbSwitch.gizmoDesc1>
  <!-- EN: Switch to rapid mode. -->
  <Milira_PlasmaPistol.comps.CompRangeWeaponVerbSwitch.gizmoDesc2>当前为散射模式，点击切换至速射模式。</Milira_PlasmaPistol.comps.CompRangeWeaponVerbSwitch.gizmoDesc2>
  <!-- EN: rapid mode -->
  <Milira_PlasmaPistol.comps.CompRangeWeaponVerbSwitch.gizmoLabel1>速射模式</Milira_PlasmaPistol.comps.CompRangeWeaponVerbSwitch.gizmoLabel1>
  <!-- EN: scatter mode -->
  <Milira_PlasmaPistol.comps.CompRangeWeaponVerbSwitch.gizmoLabel2>散射模式</Milira_PlasmaPistol.comps.CompRangeWeaponVerbSwitch.gizmoLabel2>
